{"tid":801200,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★散戶清一色沽貨 !!不理賺蝕照沽，務求要回現金","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T05:19:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"aa8acef96f362838f9ca71ce97f604118e486f3c","tid":801200,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"恒指周五早間挫約400點，騰訊控股(00700)捱沽，散戶都紛紛減持套現。致富證券大埔分行經理Gordon話，散戶見大市走勢轉差，<span style=\"color: red;\">都不理賺蝕照沽，務求要回現金</span>。<br />\n<br />\n「客戶有好多沽貨理由，例如工商銀行(01398)擬境內外共計發行最多1,000億元人民幣優先股，市場『水緊』不利股市。美國總統特朗普掀起的貿易戰可能變成『金融危機2.0』。甚至因為仔仔女女孫仔孫女下周一開學，唔得閒睇市住，沽咗貨先。」<br />\n<br />\n據其周五觀察所見，早間散戶沽出中國生物製藥(01177)、騰訊、舜宇光學科技(02382)、賭股、中國石油股份(00857)、滙豐控股(00005)、建設銀行(00939)等等，幾一致清貨套現。<br />\n<br />\n「大約是原先持有6成股票，依家減至4成、3成持貨，餘下的較多是蟹貨，橫掂都蝕很多，清唔清都冇所謂了」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=00005&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180831095926121-0831_00842_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney18.on.cc%2Ffinnews%2Frelated_news_content.html%3Flocation%3Dhk%26symbol%3D00005%26section%3Drelated_news%26article_id%3Dbkn-20180831095926121-0831_00842_001&d=kDEuW%2BW1JaXomLAtNExz50kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a58b1864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://money18.on.cc/finnews/related_news_content.html?location=hk&amp;symbol=00005&amp;section=related_news&amp;article_id=bkn-20180831095926121-0831_00842_001</a>"},{"pid":"c30ce3087f3246fe23afcab94dacfaf69bade6d3","tid":801200,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd13a1788ddabc9ec22ed2aadef4aef1f83532a","tid":801200,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":